<text top="661" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="703" left="122" width="206" height="14" font="1">The situation concerning Rwanda</text>
<text top="739" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Report of the Secretary-General pursuant to paragraph 5 of Security Council resolution 955 (1994) (S/1995/134)</text>
</page>
